data.description: Cute single level home in a desirable South Salem location.  This affordably priced, four bedroom home features updated interior paint and flooring, newer roof, and central AC.  Outside, enjoy the fantastic backyard with large deck and garden shed.  Just a block and a half away from Nelson Park and biking distance from Minto-Brown Island park.  Downtown is just 2 miles away and the Willamette River is closer than that!  Nestled in a well forrester neighborhood, Crossian Creek Scenic Trailhead is just a block away.
